WEBVTT

00:01:35.940 --> 00:01:41.089 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.180 --> 00:01:43.700 line:80%
[Episode 29]

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:48.250 line:80%
Is the Imperial Eldest Grandson
still alive?

00:01:48.510 --> 00:01:49.230 line:80%
Yes.

00:01:50.440 --> 00:01:51.390 line:80%
He's now

00:01:52.390 --> 00:01:53.920 line:80%
Lord Changxin's eldest son.

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:55.200 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai.

00:01:57.180 --> 00:02:00.020 line:80%
Who allowed you
to light a fire in this courtyard?

00:02:01.150 --> 00:02:02.670 line:80%
Are you blind?

00:02:04.130 --> 00:02:05.460 line:80%
Gouge your eyes out.

00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:07.390 line:80%
Spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:02:07.390 --> 00:02:08.230 line:80%
Get lost now!

00:02:10.040 --> 00:02:11.250 line:80%
I'll leave at once.

00:02:22.920 --> 00:02:24.390 line:80%
How dare you hit me?

00:02:24.600 --> 00:02:26.550 line:80%
For a lowly maid?

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:28.430 line:80%
In your heart, am I

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:30.390 line:80%
worth less than a lowly maid?

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:33.200 line:80%
I just don't want you to kill again.

00:02:33.270 --> 00:02:35.400 line:80%
She is a pitiful person, and so are you.

00:02:39.760 --> 00:02:41.890 line:80%
After the Jinzhou Massacre back then,

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:43.360 line:80%
Lord Changxin's wife took her eldest son,

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:44.890 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai, to the palace

00:02:45.830 --> 00:02:48.290 line:80%
to keep the widowed Crown Princess
company.

00:02:48.390 --> 00:02:51.200 line:80%
But unexpectedly,
a fire broke out in the Eastern Palace.

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:54.310 line:80%
The Crown Princess
and the Imperial Eldest Grandson

00:02:54.390 --> 00:02:55.920 line:80%
both perished in that fire.

00:02:56.550 --> 00:02:59.390 line:80%
Lord Changxin's eldest son
was severely burned.

00:02:59.950 --> 00:03:01.040 line:80%
He went into seclusion after that

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:02.570 line:80%
and never saw anyone again.

00:03:04.990 --> 00:03:07.040 line:80%
So the real Sui Yuanhuai...

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.510 line:80%
He probably died 17 years ago

00:03:10.990 --> 00:03:12.920 line:80%
in that fire at the Eastern Palace.

00:03:17.510 --> 00:03:19.160 line:80%
You say I am pitiful?

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:21.230 line:80%
Aren't you?

00:03:21.970 --> 00:03:24.310 line:80%
You are selfish, cruel,

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:26.990 line:80%
insidious, and temperamental.

00:03:26.990 --> 00:03:28.879 line:80%
Everyone who serves you
has to walk on eggshells.

00:03:28.879 --> 00:03:30.480 line:80%
One wrong move, and they die.

00:03:30.940 --> 00:03:32.830 line:80%
But all of this is your disguise.

00:03:33.430 --> 00:03:35.500 line:80%
You're just hiding your fear.

00:03:37.950 --> 00:03:39.530 line:80%
You are a pitiful person.

00:03:44.230 --> 00:03:45.770 line:80%
You also say I am pitiful.

00:03:47.390 --> 00:03:48.720 line:80%
That year when my mother

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:51.200 line:80%
pressed me into the brazier,

00:03:53.670 --> 00:03:55.200 line:80%
she also said I was pitiful.

00:03:56.510 --> 00:03:57.890 line:80%
Mother!

00:03:57.910 --> 00:03:58.890 line:80%
Min.

00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:00.830 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:00.830 --> 00:04:03.360 line:80%
Only this way can you survive.

00:04:03.880 --> 00:04:05.270 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:08.670 --> 00:04:10.800 line:80%
[Virtuous and Meritorious]

00:04:13.270 --> 00:04:14.360 line:80%
Min.

00:04:15.490 --> 00:04:16.650 line:80%
Live on.

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:27.990 line:80%
So, for all these years,

00:04:29.190 --> 00:04:31.230 line:80%
Lord Changxin has never suspected

00:04:31.670 --> 00:04:33.800 line:80%
that his eldest son has been switched?

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:36.110 line:80%
He always said

00:04:36.959 --> 00:04:39.690 line:80%
he couldn't get close
to the Eldest Young Master.

00:04:39.959 --> 00:04:42.230 line:80%
But who would suspect their own son?

00:04:43.190 --> 00:04:46.020 line:80%
The Eldest Young Master's temperament
changed drastically after the burn.

00:04:46.020 --> 00:04:47.410 line:80%
That's only natural.

00:04:48.630 --> 00:04:50.690 line:80%
It was precisely a father's instinct

00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:54.750 line:80%
that made him dislike
the Eldest Young Master from a young age.

00:04:54.750 --> 00:04:56.070 line:80%
The position of Heir Apparent

00:04:56.070 --> 00:04:58.670 line:80%
was also given to his second son,
Sui Yuanqing.

00:04:58.959 --> 00:04:59.960 line:80%
So,

00:05:01.400 --> 00:05:03.480 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing's appearance in Lin'an

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:07.290 line:80%
was also a setup
by the Imperial Eldest Grandson?

00:05:07.910 --> 00:05:10.120 line:80%
The Imperial Eldest Grandson
knew you were in Lin'an

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:11.630 line:80%
and wanted to use you

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:13.380 line:80%
to get rid of Sui Yuanqing.

00:05:14.190 --> 00:05:16.550 line:80%
The Chongzhou Army
was not yet defeated back then.

00:05:16.550 --> 00:05:17.990 line:80%
If they had taken Jizhou,

00:05:17.990 --> 00:05:20.630 line:80%
they could have marched south,
attacked the palace,

00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:22.960 line:80%
and likely forced the Emperor to abdicate.

00:05:22.960 --> 00:05:24.430 line:80%
But Sui Yuanqing is the Heir Apparent.

00:05:24.430 --> 00:05:27.070 line:80%
He'll be the only one
to inherit the throne in the future.

00:05:27.070 --> 00:05:27.990 line:80%
Therefore,

00:05:28.870 --> 00:05:32.040 line:80%
the Imperial Eldest Grandson
is bent on his death.

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:35.959 line:80%
My mother toiled all her life
for the Eastern Palace,

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:38.680 line:80%
but met a tragic end.

00:05:39.550 --> 00:05:42.959 line:80%
Qi Min even wanted to kill his own son.

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:49.040 line:80%
Crown Prince Chengde, known to the world
for his loyalty and righteousness...

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:50.280 line:80%
His descendant

00:05:50.840 --> 00:05:52.990 line:80%
is actually such an imposter,

00:05:54.190 --> 00:05:56.190 line:80%
a cold-blooded and cruel animal.

00:05:57.310 --> 00:05:59.110 line:80%
What's with Lin'an's feng shui?

00:05:59.870 --> 00:06:01.160 line:80%
First, it kept the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:03.490 line:80%
then it hid the heir
of the Eastern Palace.

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:05.230 line:80%
That Yu Qianqian,

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:07.880 line:80%
don't tell me she's someone important too.

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:11.400 line:80%
Your Lordship and Mr. Gongsun
guessed correctly.

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:14.920 line:80%
The proprietress of the Yixiang Restaurant

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:16.780 line:80%
is indeed his runaway concubine.

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:22.600 line:80%
Yu Bao'er

00:06:23.370 --> 00:06:25.230 line:80%
is the Imperial Great-Grandson.

00:06:34.190 --> 00:06:35.310 line:80%
You don't know

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:38.630 line:80%
what pain and torture I have endured

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:41.230 line:80%
to survive until today.

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:44.550 line:80%
So you inflict your pain

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:47.000 line:80%
onto others?

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:51.480 line:80%
I was born a noble,
unparalleled chosen one.

00:06:53.800 --> 00:06:55.680 line:80%
The throne of Great Yin

00:06:56.280 --> 00:06:58.060 line:80%
should have belonged to me.

00:06:58.670 --> 00:06:59.720 line:80%
But now,

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.750 line:80%
I live under a disgusting identity,

00:07:04.310 --> 00:07:06.110 line:80%
barely surviving in this world.

00:07:07.190 --> 00:07:08.750 line:80%
If Qi Min inherits

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:10.840 line:80%
the throne one day,

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:13.090 line:80%
the people will surely suffer.

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:16.360 line:80%
Your Lordship, you're a peerless hero.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.800 line:80%
If you are

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:21.310 line:80%
willing to support
the Imperial Great-Grandson's ascension,

00:07:21.310 --> 00:07:23.640 line:80%
it'll be a blessing for the common people.

00:07:28.670 --> 00:07:30.230 line:80%
Regarding the Jinzhou Massacre

00:07:30.230 --> 00:07:31.360 line:80%
17 years ago,

00:07:32.430 --> 00:07:33.830 line:80%
how much more do you know?

00:07:34.310 --> 00:07:36.110 line:80%
I don't know much.

00:07:36.550 --> 00:07:37.480 line:80%
Qi Min

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:39.840 line:80%
might know the truth.

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:42.800 line:80%
Back then,

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:46.240 line:80%
Crown Prince Chengde, who died in Jinzhou,

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:49.160 line:80%
was your father?

00:07:55.280 --> 00:07:56.040 line:80%
Yes.

00:07:58.520 --> 00:07:59.630 line:80%
I set up the trap

00:07:59.990 --> 00:08:01.790 line:80%
to force Lord Changxin to rebel,

00:08:02.070 --> 00:08:03.730 line:80%
just to seize the opportunity

00:08:04.090 --> 00:08:06.930 line:80%
to take back the empire
that belongs to me,

00:08:07.310 --> 00:08:08.550 line:80%
making Wei Yan

00:08:09.190 --> 00:08:12.070 line:80%
and everyone who killed my family

00:08:12.630 --> 00:08:14.490 line:80%
all die.

00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:23.540 line:80%
But after defeating Wei Yan,
there's the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:26.560 line:80%
What makes you think you stand a chance?

00:08:28.220 --> 00:08:29.430 line:80%
Even if I lose,

00:08:30.440 --> 00:08:32.520 line:80%
as long as I can
make the Xie and Wei families

00:08:32.520 --> 00:08:34.760 line:80%
and Lord Changxin destroy each other,

00:08:35.950 --> 00:08:37.550 line:80%
even if I die,

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:40.950 line:80%
someone will die in my place.

00:08:43.310 --> 00:08:44.430 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:50.400 line:80%
I have leverage over Lord Changxin.

00:08:53.630 --> 00:08:55.120 line:80%
This Tiger Tally

00:08:55.870 --> 00:08:58.670 line:80%
is the irrefutable proof
of the Jinzhou Massacre.

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.950 line:80%
This Tiger Tally doesn't match.

00:09:01.950 --> 00:09:02.710 line:80%
It's fake.

00:09:03.180 --> 00:09:05.680 line:80%
Your Highness, this Tiger Tally is real.

00:09:05.710 --> 00:09:07.520 line:80%
Please send troops immediately.

00:09:07.520 --> 00:09:10.160 line:80%
Crown Prince Chengde and General Xie
can't hold on much longer.

00:09:10.160 --> 00:09:11.460 line:80%
Jinzhou is in danger!

00:09:18.070 --> 00:09:19.880 line:80%
Why are you telling me these?

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:23.570 line:80%
Aren't you afraid I'll betray you?

00:09:26.310 --> 00:09:27.710 line:80%
Because I know

00:09:28.430 --> 00:09:30.040 line:80%
you are my woman.

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:32.790 line:80%
You definitely won't betray me.

00:10:02.700 --> 00:10:03.370 line:80%
Come.

00:10:06.430 --> 00:10:07.400 line:80%
Uncle Yan,

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:09.670 line:80%
I really miss my mother.

00:10:10.830 --> 00:10:11.760 line:80%
But I know,

00:10:12.250 --> 00:10:14.240 line:80%
now is not the time to save her.

00:10:15.870 --> 00:10:16.710 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:10:17.350 --> 00:10:19.120 line:80%
I've sent someone to look for her.

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:20.270 line:80%
We will find her.

00:10:20.470 --> 00:10:21.920 line:80%
Once I find your mother,

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:24.190 line:80%
I'll send you to reunite with Changning.

00:10:24.550 --> 00:10:25.350 line:80%
How do you say?

00:10:25.670 --> 00:10:28.000 line:80%
Changning has returned safely to Jizhou?

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:30.300 line:80%
What about Auntie Fan?

00:10:32.670 --> 00:10:34.920 line:80%
They are both fine.

00:10:35.950 --> 00:10:36.880 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:39.320 line:80%
They will make it back to Lin'an safely.

00:10:40.830 --> 00:10:41.470 line:80%
Go on.

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:43.240 line:80%
Hyah! Hyah!

00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:49.360 line:80%
My Lord.

00:10:50.160 --> 00:10:52.220 line:80%
We must head to Lucheng immediately.

00:10:52.920 --> 00:10:54.000 line:80%
Lord Changxin's army

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:56.400 line:80%
is likely approaching the Lucheng border.

00:10:57.640 --> 00:10:58.710 line:80%
Pass on my order.

00:10:59.040 --> 00:10:59.920 line:80%
Break camp immediately

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:01.100 line:80%
and march for Lucheng.

00:11:01.100 --> 00:11:01.830 line:80%
Yes, My Lord.

00:11:32.710 --> 00:11:33.590 line:80%
Guards!

00:11:34.310 --> 00:11:35.350 line:80%
Find the Madam.

00:11:36.160 --> 00:11:37.040 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,

00:11:37.040 --> 00:11:38.290 line:80%
Her Ladyship is missing.

00:11:38.290 --> 00:11:40.350 line:80%
I was just about to report this to you.

00:11:40.670 --> 00:11:42.520 line:80%
But I couldn't wake you up.

00:11:48.120 --> 00:11:49.240 line:80%
That bitch.

00:11:50.470 --> 00:11:52.240 line:80%
She didn't dare to poison me,

00:11:52.550 --> 00:11:54.610 line:80%
but I don't know what drug she gave me.

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:02.990 line:80%
[Lucheng Border, Jizhou]

00:12:03.070 --> 00:12:04.040 line:80%
Lucheng.

00:12:06.350 --> 00:12:08.160 line:80%
Ahead is the border of Lucheng.

00:12:11.350 --> 00:12:12.350 line:80%
Someone's there.

00:12:17.310 --> 00:12:18.280 line:80%
Qianqian!

00:12:17.960 --> 00:12:20.160 line:80%
[Lucheng Border, Jizhou]

00:12:19.070 --> 00:12:19.950 line:80%
Changyu!

00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:29.710 line:80%
Changyu.

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.440 line:80%
How did you get out?

00:12:31.830 --> 00:12:33.520 line:80%
We were just about to go look for you.

00:12:33.520 --> 00:12:35.780 line:80%
Did you think
I'd just sit and wait to die?

00:12:35.950 --> 00:12:36.830 line:80%
Let's go, quickly.

00:12:36.830 --> 00:12:38.360 line:80%
Qi will catch up any second.

00:12:49.950 --> 00:12:50.880 line:80%
Trying to run?

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:53.440 line:80%
Where do you think you're going?

00:12:53.590 --> 00:12:54.800 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:12:54.950 --> 00:12:56.640 line:80%
I can't believe you found your way here.

00:12:56.640 --> 00:12:57.810 line:80%
It's foolish,

00:12:58.180 --> 00:12:59.640 line:80%
but I admire your courage.

00:13:00.350 --> 00:13:02.710 line:80%
Kill everyone except the Madam.

00:13:16.590 --> 00:13:17.830 line:80%
He Jingyuan?

00:13:20.590 --> 00:13:21.350 line:80%
General Qi,

00:13:21.350 --> 00:13:22.550 line:80%
why are you here?

00:13:22.550 --> 00:13:24.160 line:80%
His Lordship ordered me
to protect you in secret.

00:13:24.160 --> 00:13:26.040 line:80%
He feared danger at the Lucheng border,

00:13:26.040 --> 00:13:28.160 line:80%
so he asked General He to meet us here.

00:13:29.280 --> 00:13:30.400 line:80%
Drop your weapons.

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:32.070 line:80%
Surrender now.

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:34.400 line:80%
He Jingyuan.

00:13:34.920 --> 00:13:36.580 line:80%
Do you think I'm afraid of you?

00:13:39.550 --> 00:13:40.800 line:80%
Eldest Young Master Sui,

00:13:40.800 --> 00:13:42.800 line:80%
do you intend to fight outnumbered?

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:46.580 line:80%
If you want me to let her go,

00:13:46.760 --> 00:13:48.520 line:80%
you'll have to kill me first.

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:52.000 line:80%
Retreat immediately,

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:53.660 line:80%
or I'll kill myself right now!

00:14:02.090 --> 00:14:02.900 line:80%
Retreat!

00:14:09.830 --> 00:14:10.630 line:80%
It's okay now.

00:14:11.040 --> 00:14:12.170 line:80%
Everything is fine.

00:14:15.670 --> 00:14:16.470 line:80%
Changyu,

00:14:17.000 --> 00:14:18.860 line:80%
I thought I'd never see you again.

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:22.200 line:80%
I thought about
how to escape every single day.

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:24.070 line:80%
I didn't think I'd actually succeed.

00:14:24.070 --> 00:14:25.550 line:80%
You're truly amazing.

00:14:26.310 --> 00:14:27.240 line:80%
Where is Bao'er?

00:14:28.470 --> 00:14:30.000 line:80%
Nanny Lan took Bao'er away.

00:14:31.070 --> 00:14:32.600 line:80%
But Nanny Lan is already...

00:14:34.950 --> 00:14:35.640 line:80%
General.

00:14:35.830 --> 00:14:38.120 line:80%
Sui's shadow guards
are all martial experts.

00:14:38.120 --> 00:14:39.350 line:80%
Although we had many men,

00:14:39.350 --> 00:14:41.120 line:80%
we couldn't gain any advantage.

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:42.800 line:80%
Later, the Chongzhou Army
came to support them

00:14:42.800 --> 00:14:44.260 line:80%
and covered their escape.

00:14:44.520 --> 00:14:46.190 line:80%
This man is cunning.

00:14:47.430 --> 00:14:49.670 line:80%
He must have had a backup plan.

00:14:50.950 --> 00:14:52.310 line:80%
I don't know

00:14:52.800 --> 00:14:54.330 line:80%
where Bao'er is now either.

00:14:56.070 --> 00:14:57.470 line:80%
Bao'er is blessed.

00:14:57.880 --> 00:14:59.120 line:80%
He will be safe.

00:15:08.830 --> 00:15:10.710 line:80%
Lucheng is just ahead.

00:15:10.800 --> 00:15:12.410 line:80%
Since we are already here,

00:15:12.550 --> 00:15:13.830 line:80%
there are some things

00:15:14.550 --> 00:15:16.880 line:80%
we can discuss after we return to Lucheng.

00:15:18.950 --> 00:15:20.620 line:80%
Thank you for your help, General He.

00:15:20.620 --> 00:15:23.710 line:80%
[Peace at the border]

00:15:23.740 --> 00:15:26.510 line:80%
[He]

00:15:38.350 --> 00:15:39.120 line:80%
General.

00:15:41.950 --> 00:15:42.880 line:80%
You're here.

00:15:49.830 --> 00:15:51.030 line:80%
Greetings, General.

00:15:51.400 --> 00:15:53.070 line:80%
Thank you for saving me yesterday,
General.

00:15:53.070 --> 00:15:54.800 line:80%
No need to thank me.

00:15:55.430 --> 00:15:57.040 line:80%
The whole army is saying

00:15:57.040 --> 00:15:59.500 line:80%
that you killed Shi Hu
with 3 hammer strikes.

00:15:59.760 --> 00:16:00.550 line:80%
Is it true?

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:02.760 line:80%
Two strikes.

00:16:06.670 --> 00:16:08.310 line:80%
I have always loved martial arts.

00:16:08.310 --> 00:16:11.280 line:80%
Would you spar with me for a few rounds?

00:16:11.280 --> 00:16:12.880 line:80%
My skills are amateurish.

00:16:11.830 --> 00:16:14.500 line:80%
[Qinwen Hall]

00:16:13.070 --> 00:16:14.710 line:80%
I can't compare to you.

00:16:14.920 --> 00:16:16.640 line:80%
Whether you can compare or not,

00:16:16.640 --> 00:16:18.640 line:80%
we'll know after we fight.

00:16:20.710 --> 00:16:21.280 line:80%
Come on.

00:16:23.550 --> 00:16:24.480 line:80%
Give it your all.

00:16:24.670 --> 00:16:25.640 line:80%
Don't hold back.

00:16:40.480 --> 00:16:44.260 line:80%
♪ The world is vast ♪

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:50.490 line:80%
♪ The storm is rising ♪

00:16:52.960 --> 00:16:56.700 line:80%
♪ Day and night ♪

00:16:57.690 --> 00:17:01.250 line:80%
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

00:17:04.919 --> 00:17:09.280 line:80%
♪ All people ♪

00:17:10.560 --> 00:17:15.830 line:80%
♪ Are part of the past ♪

00:17:11.970 --> 00:17:12.990 line:80%
[Qinwen Hall]

00:17:14.090 --> 00:17:15.919 line:80%
[Loyalty and Fortitude]

00:17:15.919 --> 00:17:21.119 line:80%
[17 years ago]

00:17:16.290 --> 00:17:20.919 line:80%
♪ What's the date today? ♪

00:17:21.350 --> 00:17:25.230 line:80%
♪ How lamentable ♪

00:17:34.980 --> 00:17:39.620 line:80%
♪ What's the date today? ♪

00:17:39.810 --> 00:17:46.420 line:80%
[Loyalty and Fortitude]

00:17:40.290 --> 00:17:43.490 line:80%
♪ How lamentable ♪

00:17:46.490 --> 00:17:50.030 line:80%
[Qinwen Hall]

00:17:46.680 --> 00:17:48.520 line:80%
Do you know where the flaw was

00:17:48.830 --> 00:17:50.240 line:80%
in that move just now?

00:17:52.040 --> 00:17:53.770 line:80%
Please enlighten me, General.

00:17:56.040 --> 00:17:57.310 line:80%
You've practiced

00:17:57.310 --> 00:17:59.720 line:80%
this blade technique for too long.

00:17:59.830 --> 00:18:01.630 line:80%
Your strikes are too rigid.

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:04.480 line:80%
You just follow one move with another.

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:06.310 line:80%
But on the battlefield,

00:18:06.480 --> 00:18:09.390 line:80%
the enemy's moves change in an instant.

00:18:09.390 --> 00:18:12.150 line:80%
If one strike fails,
just switch to another.

00:18:12.150 --> 00:18:14.000 line:80%
Don't lose your cool

00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:16.530 line:80%
just because someone
sees through your move.

00:18:20.110 --> 00:18:21.240 line:80%
Thank you, General.

00:18:22.590 --> 00:18:25.150 line:80%
But my father taught me
this blade technique.

00:18:25.150 --> 00:18:26.910 line:80%
My father never revealed his skills

00:18:26.910 --> 00:18:28.170 line:80%
in front of outsiders.

00:18:29.110 --> 00:18:30.070 line:80%
But General,

00:18:30.390 --> 00:18:32.000 line:80%
why are you so familiar with it

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:33.730 line:80%
and able to counter every move?

00:18:36.720 --> 00:18:38.070 line:80%
Your father and I

00:18:39.150 --> 00:18:40.310 line:80%
were old friends.

00:18:47.830 --> 00:18:48.630 line:80%
He.

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:50.870 line:80%
Your spear technique has improved a lot.

00:18:50.870 --> 00:18:52.110 line:80%
You are just as good.

00:18:52.960 --> 00:18:54.290 line:80%
Do you have a successor?

00:18:54.870 --> 00:18:55.680 line:80%
Wei.

00:18:55.680 --> 00:18:58.550 line:80%
You are mocking me
for being all alone again.

00:18:58.800 --> 00:19:00.480 line:80%
How can I compare to you?

00:19:00.480 --> 00:19:02.350 line:80%
You have a virtuous wife
and a filial daughter.

00:19:02.350 --> 00:19:04.550 line:80%
Are you planning
to pass your blade technique

00:19:04.550 --> 00:19:06.480 line:80%
to that little girl of yours?

00:19:06.480 --> 00:19:08.870 line:80%
Whether my little girl
inherits my blade technique

00:19:08.870 --> 00:19:09.870 line:80%
is unknown.

00:19:09.870 --> 00:19:10.760 line:80%
However,

00:19:10.910 --> 00:19:12.440 line:80%
my little girl's stride

00:19:12.590 --> 00:19:14.150 line:80%
is so full of vigor.

00:19:14.150 --> 00:19:15.760 line:80%
She's got my style.

00:19:15.830 --> 00:19:17.030 line:80%
She's got your style?

00:19:21.390 --> 00:19:22.830 line:80%
She's doomed, totally.

00:19:22.910 --> 00:19:23.960 line:80%
If she's like you,

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:25.620 line:80%
how will she ever get married?

00:19:26.760 --> 00:19:28.020 line:80%
She's like her mother,

00:19:28.240 --> 00:19:29.240 line:80%
very pretty.

00:19:30.390 --> 00:19:32.150 line:80%
But she has my build.

00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:34.830 line:80%
If she can inherit my blade technique,

00:19:35.110 --> 00:19:36.110 line:80%
then in this world,

00:19:36.110 --> 00:19:38.160 line:80%
no man will be worthy of her.

00:19:39.720 --> 00:19:42.110 line:80%
My father never mentioned it to me.

00:19:43.040 --> 00:19:44.310 line:80%
Besides, my father was just

00:19:44.310 --> 00:19:46.280 line:80%
a butcher in Lin'an.

00:19:46.830 --> 00:19:49.200 line:80%
How could he be friends with a general?

00:19:49.310 --> 00:19:50.630 line:80%
It's a long story.

00:19:52.110 --> 00:19:54.110 line:80%
Once the siege of Lucheng is lifted,

00:19:54.960 --> 00:19:56.240 line:80%
I'll tell you.

00:20:02.280 --> 00:20:02.910 line:80%
General.

00:20:03.440 --> 00:20:05.800 line:80%
Since there have never been
female generals in the camp,

00:20:05.800 --> 00:20:07.110 line:80%
I thought,

00:20:07.110 --> 00:20:09.680 line:80%
those suits of armor might not fit you,

00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:12.910 line:80%
so I had a suit custom-made for you.

00:20:14.070 --> 00:20:15.240 line:80%
May it accompany you

00:20:15.350 --> 00:20:17.200 line:80%
to gain fame and glory.

00:20:18.280 --> 00:20:19.410 line:80%
Thank you, General!

00:20:22.550 --> 00:20:24.680 line:80%
The last time I gifted armor to someone

00:20:25.320 --> 00:20:27.720 line:80%
was 30 years ago.

00:20:28.830 --> 00:20:29.800 line:80%
It's a pity

00:20:30.870 --> 00:20:32.440 line:80%
that he is no longer with us.

00:20:36.590 --> 00:20:37.800 line:80%
Your old friend

00:20:37.800 --> 00:20:39.000 line:80%
must have been a hero

00:20:39.200 --> 00:20:40.800 line:80%
who died on the battlefield.

00:20:43.800 --> 00:20:46.070 line:80%
Although he didn't rest eternally

00:20:46.070 --> 00:20:48.550 line:80%
on a sandy battlefield,

00:20:49.110 --> 00:20:52.070 line:80%
he stopped an unjust army.

00:20:52.680 --> 00:20:54.540 line:80%
For the sake of the common people,

00:20:54.910 --> 00:20:57.310 line:80%
he sacrificed his life for righteousness.

00:20:58.150 --> 00:20:59.040 line:80%
In the end,

00:21:00.590 --> 00:21:02.630 line:80%
only his loyal bones remained.

00:21:06.830 --> 00:21:08.000 line:80%
My father said,

00:21:08.760 --> 00:21:10.290 line:80%
everyone dies eventually,

00:21:10.680 --> 00:21:12.630 line:80%
but if one can benefit the living,

00:21:13.390 --> 00:21:14.790 line:80%
their life is not in vain.

00:21:16.760 --> 00:21:18.630 line:80%
Don't be too sad, General.

00:21:18.870 --> 00:21:20.470 line:80%
Please restrain your grief.

00:21:25.680 --> 00:21:26.150 line:80%
Master, I heard you were

00:21:26.150 --> 00:21:28.610 line:80%
sparring with the heroine
who killed Shi Hu.

00:21:28.830 --> 00:21:31.290 line:80%
I couldn't make it in time
to watch and learn.

00:21:31.630 --> 00:21:32.870 line:80%
Lord Menkan.

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:35.280 line:80%
I knew it was you from your voice.

00:21:36.200 --> 00:21:37.350 line:80%
I guessed it was you.

00:21:39.040 --> 00:21:39.770 line:80%
How did it go?

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:41.130 line:80%
Finished so soon?

00:21:41.520 --> 00:21:43.040 line:80%
What's the result?

00:21:43.480 --> 00:21:44.890 line:80%
When has your courtesy name

00:21:44.890 --> 00:21:47.090 line:80%
changed to Menkan?

00:21:49.070 --> 00:21:50.060 line:80%
Don't laugh at me, Master.

00:21:50.060 --> 00:21:52.150 line:80%
Life is either inside
or outside the threshold.

00:21:52.150 --> 00:21:53.310 line:80%
It's just a name.

00:21:55.150 --> 00:21:56.870 line:80%
Did I say something wrong?

00:21:58.590 --> 00:22:00.150 line:80%
Say whatever you want.

00:22:00.150 --> 00:22:00.950 line:80%
It's up to you.

00:22:03.630 --> 00:22:04.910 line:80%
Li Huai'an.

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:06.200 line:80%
Li Menkan.

00:22:06.390 --> 00:22:07.440 line:80%
Captain Li.

00:22:08.110 --> 00:22:10.240 line:80%
Educated people sure have many names.

00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:13.770 line:80%
But my godfather just gave me
a courtesy name too.

00:22:14.310 --> 00:22:15.710 line:80%
You mean Grand Tutor Tao?

00:22:17.280 --> 00:22:18.520 line:80%
Grand Tutor Tao?

00:22:19.480 --> 00:22:21.720 line:80%
When did he become your godfather?

00:22:22.310 --> 00:22:23.680 line:80%
Just a few days ago.

00:22:23.680 --> 00:22:24.910 line:80%
He even gave me a courtesy name.

00:22:24.910 --> 00:22:25.680 line:80%
It's...

00:22:27.310 --> 00:22:28.310 line:80%
It's Shanjun.

00:22:28.590 --> 00:22:29.870 line:80%
It means tigress.

00:22:29.870 --> 00:22:32.070 line:80%
From now on, you can call me Fan Tigress.

00:22:35.480 --> 00:22:37.520 line:80%
Have you gotten used to life
in the camp recently?

00:22:37.520 --> 00:22:39.110 line:80%
I didn't expect you to be so skilled.

00:22:39.110 --> 00:22:41.080 line:80%
You've achieved so much in the camp.

00:22:41.080 --> 00:22:43.630 line:80%
I'm afraid you'll outshine
the Marquis of Wu'an in the future.

00:22:43.630 --> 00:22:45.160 line:80%
Is he coming to Lucheng too?

00:22:46.830 --> 00:22:49.150 line:80%
This is a military matter.
Naturally, I know.

00:22:49.150 --> 00:22:52.310 line:80%
General Xie,
to avoid the enemy's surveillance,

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:53.960 line:80%
likely took a detour.

00:22:54.310 --> 00:22:56.770 line:80%
But he should be arriving
in a couple of days.

00:22:56.870 --> 00:22:58.390 line:80%
General He just told me

00:22:59.150 --> 00:23:01.280 line:80%
that he and my father were old friends.

00:23:01.680 --> 00:23:03.340 line:80%
Do you know what this is about?

00:23:05.910 --> 00:23:07.440 line:80%
I wanted to ask for details,

00:23:07.520 --> 00:23:08.920 line:80%
but he wouldn't say much.

00:23:09.550 --> 00:23:11.050 line:80%
Grandfather once told me

00:23:11.550 --> 00:23:12.350 line:80%
that my father

00:23:12.800 --> 00:23:14.280 line:80%
borrowed Fan Erniu's identity

00:23:14.280 --> 00:23:15.630 line:80%
to survive in Lin'an.

00:23:16.240 --> 00:23:18.200 line:80%
But the Jizhou records clearly state

00:23:18.200 --> 00:23:21.060 line:80%
that my father was just a butcher
killed by bandits.

00:23:23.440 --> 00:23:24.760 line:80%
Why do I feel like

00:23:25.070 --> 00:23:26.830 line:80%
everyone is lying?

00:23:27.630 --> 00:23:29.090 line:80%
Yet what everyone says...

00:23:31.910 --> 00:23:33.370 line:80%
also seems like the truth.

00:23:36.310 --> 00:23:38.150 line:80%
Since Master isn't willing to talk deeply,

00:23:38.150 --> 00:23:39.760 line:80%
he must have his reasons.

00:23:41.310 --> 00:23:43.000 line:80%
The fact that he calls your father
an old friend

00:23:43.000 --> 00:23:44.200 line:80%
speaks volumes about

00:23:44.240 --> 00:23:45.390 line:80%
what an admirable man

00:23:45.390 --> 00:23:46.520 line:80%
your father was.

00:23:50.800 --> 00:23:52.060 line:80%
Hearing what you said,

00:23:52.150 --> 00:23:53.390 line:80%
I feel much better.

00:23:57.630 --> 00:23:59.030 line:80%
Lucheng is so beautiful.

00:24:00.310 --> 00:24:02.390 line:80%
Will it soon end up like Lin'an,

00:24:02.800 --> 00:24:04.660 line:80%
suffering from the flames of war?

00:24:06.760 --> 00:24:08.960 line:80%
It's about time you returned to Lin'an.

00:24:09.000 --> 00:24:11.240 line:80%
Changning and Mrs. Zhao
are waiting for you at home.

00:24:11.240 --> 00:24:12.240 line:80%
I can go home?

00:24:12.240 --> 00:24:15.840 line:80%
I'll send someone to escort you
out of the city in a couple of days.

00:24:16.720 --> 00:24:17.350 line:80%
Alright.

00:24:18.110 --> 00:24:19.280 line:80%
I observed the stars at night.

00:24:19.280 --> 00:24:20.390 line:80%
Wuqu (the Martial Star) fades its light.

00:24:20.390 --> 00:24:21.350 line:80%
Pojun (the Vanquisher Star)
drags its shadow.

00:24:21.350 --> 00:24:22.610 line:80%
In the Lucheng sector,

00:24:22.910 --> 00:24:25.040 line:80%
there will be bloodshed within 3 days.

00:24:26.440 --> 00:24:28.070 line:80%
Let's feign an attack first

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:30.700 line:80%
to draw out their main force.

00:24:30.760 --> 00:24:31.950 line:80%
Then we'll use a move

00:24:31.980 --> 00:24:33.700 line:80%
to trap them like rats.

00:24:35.870 --> 00:24:37.350 line:80%
That's what the omens say.

00:24:37.870 --> 00:24:39.150 line:80%
But in my opinion,

00:24:39.550 --> 00:24:40.830 line:80%
we should concentrate our forces

00:24:40.830 --> 00:24:42.090 line:80%
and strike at the heart

00:24:42.590 --> 00:24:44.050 line:80%
to capture that old thief.

00:24:48.910 --> 00:24:50.710 line:80%
As expected of you, Xie Jiuheng.

00:24:50.960 --> 00:24:52.440 line:80%
So direct.

00:24:52.720 --> 00:24:54.200 line:80%
Others might have the ambition,

00:24:54.200 --> 00:24:55.860 line:80%
but they don't have your guts.

00:24:57.000 --> 00:24:58.480 line:80%
Even if Shi Yue dares to think of it,

00:24:58.480 --> 00:25:00.350 line:80%
he won't believe you'd actually do it.

00:25:00.350 --> 00:25:01.590 line:80%
However, this plan

00:25:01.800 --> 00:25:03.860 line:80%
will leave Lucheng's gate wide open.

00:25:04.800 --> 00:25:06.830 line:80%
I fear Lucheng won't be able to hold.

00:25:07.480 --> 00:25:08.960 line:80%
Go inform Old General He.

00:25:19.680 --> 00:25:21.990 line:80%
I have to say,
the fish here are quite big.

00:25:22.110 --> 00:25:22.830 line:80%
Right?

00:25:23.110 --> 00:25:23.910 line:80%
Big, aren't they?

00:25:23.910 --> 00:25:24.390 line:80%
Here.

00:25:25.150 --> 00:25:27.910 line:80%
Here. Add some herbs
to remove the fishy smell. Here.

00:25:27.910 --> 00:25:29.770 line:80%
Are you asking for a kicking, boy?

00:25:30.520 --> 00:25:31.200 line:80%
Godfather,

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:34.440 line:80%
-how did you know we are here?
-Let's grill for a while.

00:25:34.720 --> 00:25:38.960 line:80%
To get the fish to bite, of course.

00:25:42.910 --> 00:25:44.410 line:80%
Are you going to ask me

00:25:45.000 --> 00:25:46.860 line:80%
if I still want to stay in the army?

00:25:48.550 --> 00:25:49.830 line:80%
Since you asked,

00:25:50.040 --> 00:25:51.680 line:80%
do you regret it?

00:25:52.070 --> 00:25:53.870 line:80%
Do you want me to teach you

00:25:53.890 --> 00:25:57.220 line:80%
the skills to be a match
for ten thousand on the battlefield?

00:25:59.800 --> 00:26:00.680 line:80%
I do.

00:26:02.910 --> 00:26:03.720 line:80%
And I don't.

00:26:06.150 --> 00:26:07.830 line:80%
What kind of nonsense is that?

00:26:08.040 --> 00:26:09.800 line:80%
You're hopeless.

00:26:11.760 --> 00:26:12.550 line:80%
Godfather,

00:26:13.520 --> 00:26:15.980 line:80%
it's not that I don't want
to stay in the army.

00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:17.680 line:80%
It's just that...

00:26:19.630 --> 00:26:22.290 line:80%
I don't want to lead troops
into battle anymore.

00:26:22.350 --> 00:26:25.010 line:80%
I don't want to see anyone else
die in front of me.

00:26:26.520 --> 00:26:28.380 line:80%
Fan just wants to go back to Lin'an

00:26:28.440 --> 00:26:30.000 line:80%
and live a normal life.

00:26:30.520 --> 00:26:31.630 line:80%
Why do you keep pushing her?

00:26:31.630 --> 00:26:32.440 line:80%
Exactly.

00:26:34.630 --> 00:26:36.830 line:80%
You are all good people.

00:26:37.830 --> 00:26:41.310 line:80%
But that is only a small kindness.

00:26:41.870 --> 00:26:45.760 line:80%
Don't you know that no egg is unbroken
when the nest falls?

00:26:46.070 --> 00:26:47.680 line:80%
The massacre of Lin'an Town

00:26:48.000 --> 00:26:50.240 line:80%
is the best proof.

00:26:53.200 --> 00:26:54.720 line:80%
Lord Changxin rebelled

00:26:55.720 --> 00:26:57.110 line:80%
and led his troops south.

00:26:57.110 --> 00:26:58.200 line:80%
It's murder.

00:26:58.680 --> 00:27:01.590 line:80%
The Imperial Court besieged Lord Changxin.

00:27:01.590 --> 00:27:03.070 line:80%
It's also murder.

00:27:03.800 --> 00:27:04.590 line:80%
Changyu,

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:06.310 line:80%
think about it.

00:27:06.310 --> 00:27:09.200 line:80%
How are they different?

00:27:14.150 --> 00:27:15.390 line:80%
I only know

00:27:15.960 --> 00:27:17.820 line:80%
that although I killed soldiers,

00:27:18.590 --> 00:27:21.260 line:80%
they might have been just like us before,

00:27:22.280 --> 00:27:24.810 line:80%
just commoners
thrown onto the battlefield.

00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:29.480 line:80%
Once war begins,

00:27:29.760 --> 00:27:33.630 line:80%
what is the difference
between soldiers and commoners?

00:27:35.070 --> 00:27:38.070 line:80%
Mobilizing an army
incurs huge expenditure.

00:27:38.440 --> 00:27:40.150 line:80%
The cost of one soldier

00:27:40.390 --> 00:27:42.720 line:80%
requires the labor of 10 civilians.

00:27:43.110 --> 00:27:44.550 line:80%
The longer the war lasts,

00:27:44.910 --> 00:27:47.280 line:80%
the harder it is for the people.

00:27:48.000 --> 00:27:49.800 line:80%
Corpses of the starved line the roads,

00:27:49.800 --> 00:27:51.800 line:80%
and refugees come one after another.

00:27:51.800 --> 00:27:53.060 line:80%
Therefore, it is said,

00:27:53.070 --> 00:27:55.520 line:80%
"What is essential in war is victory,
not prolonged operations."

00:27:55.520 --> 00:27:58.350 line:80%
To end the war with the fewest casualties,

00:27:58.870 --> 00:28:00.440 line:80%
even if one kills,

00:28:01.000 --> 00:28:04.000 line:80%
it is still an act of great benevolence.

00:28:17.830 --> 00:28:20.200 line:80%
I'll give you a weapon
to protect yourself.

00:28:20.200 --> 00:28:22.400 line:80%
Your butcher knife is no longer usable.

00:28:22.550 --> 00:28:24.590 line:80%
I melted it down and reforged it

00:28:25.200 --> 00:28:26.660 line:80%
to make these dual blades.

00:28:27.310 --> 00:28:29.110 line:80%
I never properly gave you a gift.

00:28:29.520 --> 00:28:31.870 line:80%
These dual blades suit you perfectly.

00:28:33.760 --> 00:28:35.890 line:80%
You forgot. You did give me something.

00:28:36.310 --> 00:28:38.630 line:80%
The bracers you gave me are great.

00:28:41.240 --> 00:28:42.810 line:80%
Why do I smell blood?

00:28:49.200 --> 00:28:50.200 line:80%
Are you injured?

00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:51.040 line:80%
No.

00:28:51.440 --> 00:28:52.590 line:80%
It's an old injury.

00:28:53.080 --> 00:28:53.930 line:80%
You're lying.

00:28:53.960 --> 00:28:55.280 line:80%
You were fine a few days ago.

00:28:55.280 --> 00:28:56.760 line:80%
How could an old injury relapse today?

00:28:56.760 --> 00:28:57.760 line:80%
Let me see.

00:28:57.760 --> 00:28:59.280 line:80%
Just some minor injuries. I'm fine.

00:28:59.280 --> 00:29:00.000 line:80%
If you don't show them to me,

00:29:00.000 --> 00:29:01.200 line:80%
you should leave now.

00:29:09.480 --> 00:29:10.610 line:80%
How did you get hurt?

00:29:11.350 --> 00:29:12.240 line:80%
Who hurt you?

00:29:14.760 --> 00:29:15.720 line:80%
Well...

00:29:17.390 --> 00:29:18.390 line:80%
I baptized the blade with blood.

00:29:18.390 --> 00:29:19.550 line:80%
Are you crazy?

00:29:34.760 --> 00:29:36.890 line:80%
Have you been reading too many novels?

00:29:37.150 --> 00:29:39.080 line:80%
You think I'd be so touched I'd cry?

00:29:41.590 --> 00:29:42.720 line:80%
If it happens again,

00:29:43.070 --> 00:29:44.310 line:80%
I'll buy 100 blades

00:29:44.680 --> 00:29:47.080 line:80%
and let you cut yourself
as much as you want.

00:29:47.220 --> 00:29:48.240 line:80%
If your arms are not enough,

00:29:48.240 --> 00:29:49.440 line:80%
you can use your butt.

00:30:01.590 --> 00:30:02.310 line:80%
Changyu,

00:30:02.660 --> 00:30:05.210 line:80%
do you remember
back at the Wushan barracks,

00:30:05.390 --> 00:30:08.150 line:80%
when I had you hunt down those 3 scouts?

00:30:08.150 --> 00:30:10.530 line:80%
If you had been merciful then

00:30:10.590 --> 00:30:12.830 line:80%
and let those 3 scouts go,

00:30:12.830 --> 00:30:16.870 line:80%
Lucheng would have been the one to suffer.

00:30:17.910 --> 00:30:21.680 line:80%
The casualties
would have been far heavier.

00:30:33.520 --> 00:30:34.390 line:80%
I understand.

00:30:34.600 --> 00:30:36.660 line:80%
Thank you for the lesson, Godfather.

00:30:52.150 --> 00:30:52.800 line:80%
My Lady.

00:30:53.390 --> 00:30:54.760 line:80%
It came from the falcon.

00:30:54.760 --> 00:30:56.110 line:80%
His Lordship says
Yu Bao'er has been found.

00:30:56.110 --> 00:30:58.040 line:80%
He's already being sent to Lin'an.

00:30:59.000 --> 00:30:59.830 line:80%
That's great.

00:31:00.520 --> 00:31:01.350 line:80%
Now Qianqian

00:31:01.350 --> 00:31:04.350 line:80%
can return to Lin'an in peace
and reunite with Bao'er.

00:31:05.110 --> 00:31:06.280 line:80%
Let's pack up, too.

00:31:06.350 --> 00:31:07.720 line:80%
We'll leave tomorrow morning.

00:31:07.720 --> 00:31:08.310 line:80%
Yes.

00:31:09.180 --> 00:31:11.850 line:80%
[Lucheng Inn]

00:31:09.680 --> 00:31:11.550 line:80%
I just visited General He.

00:31:11.800 --> 00:31:14.910 line:80%
Manager Yu, knowing you and Mrs. Fan
are returning to Lin'an,

00:31:14.910 --> 00:31:16.640 line:80%
I came specifically to see you.

00:31:18.110 --> 00:31:19.310 line:80%
Changyu told me.

00:31:19.960 --> 00:31:21.070 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Gongsun,

00:31:21.070 --> 00:31:23.110 line:80%
and His Lordship, for saving Bao'er.

00:31:23.110 --> 00:31:24.510 line:80%
I am endlessly grateful.

00:31:25.870 --> 00:31:26.830 line:80%
Please accept my bow.

00:31:26.830 --> 00:31:27.760 line:80%
No, no, don't.

00:31:27.870 --> 00:31:29.350 line:80%
Manager Yu, you're too kind.

00:31:29.350 --> 00:31:29.960 line:80%
Sit.

00:31:37.440 --> 00:31:40.200 line:80%
I've heard Changyu speak of you.

00:31:40.910 --> 00:31:42.070 line:80%
War is imminent.

00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:44.040 line:80%
For you to come all this way, Mr. Gongsun,

00:31:44.040 --> 00:31:46.040 line:80%
it must be for something important.

00:31:47.590 --> 00:31:48.390 line:80%
Yes.

00:31:52.240 --> 00:31:53.240 line:80%
You may leave now.

00:31:57.870 --> 00:31:59.480 line:80%
Lord Changxin's eldest son,

00:32:00.150 --> 00:32:02.960 line:80%
or rather, the Imperial Eldest Grandson
of the former Eastern Palace—

00:32:02.960 --> 00:32:05.110 line:80%
do you know anything about him?

00:32:07.630 --> 00:32:09.030 line:80%
What brought us together

00:32:09.240 --> 00:32:11.350 line:80%
was nothing but a doomed, cursed bond.

00:32:11.350 --> 00:32:14.520 line:80%
I regret that when he was drowning
and near death,

00:32:14.680 --> 00:32:15.940 line:80%
I acted out of kindness

00:32:16.070 --> 00:32:18.150 line:80%
and saved him
with mouth-to-mouth resuscitation.

00:32:18.150 --> 00:32:19.630 line:80%
I didn't expect to invite trouble.

00:32:19.630 --> 00:32:22.630 line:80%
That is what led to
all the subsequent entanglements.

00:32:25.870 --> 00:32:28.050 line:80%
He holds a Tiger Tally.

00:32:28.350 --> 00:32:31.950 line:80%
He claims it is irrefutable proof
of Lord Changxin's intention to rebel.

00:32:31.950 --> 00:32:33.200 line:80%
But as far as I know,

00:32:33.440 --> 00:32:36.070 line:80%
Lord Changxin
doesn't know his true identity.

00:32:36.200 --> 00:32:37.240 line:80%
Tiger Tally?

00:32:40.550 --> 00:32:42.610 line:80%
They are estranged as father and son.

00:32:42.720 --> 00:32:44.520 line:80%
He hates Lord Changxin deeply.

00:32:45.000 --> 00:32:47.630 line:80%
He is bent on setting a trap
to force Lord Changxin to rebel,

00:32:47.630 --> 00:32:50.560 line:80%
so he can seize the opportunity
to retake the throne.

00:32:52.350 --> 00:32:54.410 line:80%
No wonder he wanted
to kill Yu Bao'er.

00:32:55.280 --> 00:32:58.000 line:80%
The Imperial Eldest Grandson
uses Lord Changxin's rebellion

00:32:58.000 --> 00:32:59.150 line:80%
to seize the throne,

00:33:00.680 --> 00:33:04.340 line:80%
so how could he tolerate
the existence of other legitimate heirs?

00:33:04.550 --> 00:33:05.910 line:80%
Thank you for telling me, Manager Yu.

00:33:05.910 --> 00:33:06.760 line:80%
The situation is urgent.

00:33:06.760 --> 00:33:07.870 line:80%
I must go now.

00:33:08.920 --> 00:33:09.720 line:80%
Farewell.

00:33:14.910 --> 00:33:15.630 line:80%
Manager Yu.

00:33:16.150 --> 00:33:18.870 line:80%
The mouth-to-mouth resuscitation
you just mentioned,

00:33:18.870 --> 00:33:20.470 line:80%
what kind of technique is it?

00:33:22.200 --> 00:33:25.010 line:80%
It's just a folk remedy from my hometown.

00:33:25.110 --> 00:33:27.070 line:80%
You pass air mouth-to-mouth

00:33:27.070 --> 00:33:28.590 line:80%
and press on the chest over the heart.

00:33:28.590 --> 00:33:30.520 line:80%
It can save lives in critical moments.

00:33:30.520 --> 00:33:31.870 line:80%
I see.

00:33:32.590 --> 00:33:35.830 line:80%
It is also recorded
in the "Treatise on Cold Damage Diseases."

00:33:35.830 --> 00:33:36.910 line:80%
However,

00:33:37.070 --> 00:33:39.970 line:80%
the mouth-to-mouth method
is slightly different.

00:33:40.280 --> 00:33:43.880 line:80%
It really risks violating the boundaries
between men and women.

00:33:48.130 --> 00:33:49.480 line:80%
Manager Yu, you are righteous.

00:33:49.480 --> 00:33:51.740 line:80%
I have learned something new. Farewell.

00:33:55.450 --> 00:33:56.150 line:80%
Wenkan.

00:33:56.520 --> 00:33:59.310 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an plans
to lead the main force of the Yanzhou Army

00:33:59.310 --> 00:34:02.910 line:80%
straight to Lord Changxin's main tent
in Luocheng.

00:34:04.110 --> 00:34:06.040 line:80%
Luocheng is Lord Changxin's base.

00:34:06.200 --> 00:34:07.730 line:80%
It must be heavily guarded.

00:34:08.680 --> 00:34:11.160 line:80%
I don't think the Marquis of Wu'an
can succeed with such forces.

00:34:11.160 --> 00:34:15.680 line:80%
So I want you to personally lead
3,000 elite troops

00:34:17.160 --> 00:34:19.160 line:80%
and split into multiple routes
to provide cover,

00:34:19.160 --> 00:34:22.620 line:80%
helping the Marquis of Wu'an
strike straight at their center.

00:34:22.640 --> 00:34:25.420 line:80%
Only then will there be
a chance of success.

00:34:25.910 --> 00:34:27.370 line:80%
But the Lucheng garrison,

00:34:27.910 --> 00:34:29.390 line:80%
excluding the Yanzhou Army
and the Xie Army,

00:34:29.390 --> 00:34:30.850 line:80%
has no more than 5,000 men.

00:34:31.310 --> 00:34:32.910 line:80%
Master, if you give me 3,000,

00:34:33.120 --> 00:34:34.310 line:80%
how will you defend the city?

00:34:34.310 --> 00:34:35.800 line:80%
Even with the combined force of 5,000 men,

00:34:35.800 --> 00:34:39.030 line:80%
can we hold off
Lord Changxin's army of 50,000?

00:34:39.760 --> 00:34:41.030 line:80%
In the Battle of Lucheng,

00:34:41.030 --> 00:34:43.030 line:80%
we must use surprise tactics.

00:34:44.120 --> 00:34:44.990 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:34:45.310 --> 00:34:46.120 line:80%
I will

00:34:47.160 --> 00:34:48.510 line:80%
defend Lucheng.

00:34:51.800 --> 00:34:53.120 line:80%
I, Li Huai'an,
Martial Commandant of Jizhou,

00:34:53.120 --> 00:34:54.120 line:80%
accept the order.

00:34:55.610 --> 00:34:59.360 line:80%
[Lucheng]

00:34:56.080 --> 00:34:57.950 line:80%
It is so good to have found Bao'er.

00:34:58.430 --> 00:34:59.680 line:80%
It is all thanks to Yan Zheng.

00:34:59.680 --> 00:35:01.720 line:80%
I will remember this favor.

00:35:02.200 --> 00:35:02.910 line:80%
Fan,

00:35:03.600 --> 00:35:04.510 line:80%
look who it is.

00:35:05.390 --> 00:35:06.200 line:80%
Changyu.

00:35:06.640 --> 00:35:08.870 line:80%
Kang Xiaodan, why are you here?

00:35:08.960 --> 00:35:11.940 line:80%
[Kang Xiaodan, Grandson of Granny Kang]

00:35:09.120 --> 00:35:10.640 line:80%
Lord Li heard I was from Lin'an,

00:35:10.640 --> 00:35:12.170 line:80%
so he let me go back with you.

00:35:13.830 --> 00:35:15.490 line:80%
I heard about my grandmother.

00:35:17.030 --> 00:35:19.290 line:80%
Thank you for giving her a proper burial.

00:35:21.200 --> 00:35:22.240 line:80%
We are both from Lin'an.

00:35:22.240 --> 00:35:23.510 line:80%
There is no need for thanks.

00:35:23.510 --> 00:35:25.640 line:80%
It's perfect. Let's go back together.

00:35:31.600 --> 00:35:32.310 line:80%
General,

00:35:33.030 --> 00:35:34.290 line:80%
we are about to depart.

00:35:34.990 --> 00:35:36.430 line:80%
I wish you a great victory, General.

00:35:36.430 --> 00:35:38.090 line:80%
I will wait for your good news.

00:35:39.760 --> 00:35:41.390 line:80%
If we are destined to meet again,

00:35:41.390 --> 00:35:43.050 line:80%
I ask you to resolve my doubts.

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:45.160 line:80%
If I am lucky enough

00:35:45.160 --> 00:35:47.030 line:80%
to survive along with Lucheng,

00:35:47.030 --> 00:35:48.290 line:80%
I will certainly

00:35:48.760 --> 00:35:50.290 line:80%
tell you everything I know.

00:35:53.390 --> 00:35:54.160 line:80%
Thank you.

00:35:56.600 --> 00:35:57.240 line:80%
Let's go.

00:36:04.310 --> 00:36:05.120 line:80%
He,

00:36:05.120 --> 00:36:06.830 line:80%
the Northwest frontier is desolate.

00:36:06.830 --> 00:36:08.600 line:80%
Jinzhou, Chongzhou, and Jizhou

00:36:08.600 --> 00:36:09.910 line:80%
are particularly barren.

00:36:09.910 --> 00:36:12.310 line:80%
You must take care of yourself
on this trip.

00:36:12.950 --> 00:36:15.760 line:80%
A good man should establish himself.

00:36:16.080 --> 00:36:17.910 line:80%
It is better than being in the Capital,

00:36:17.910 --> 00:36:19.430 line:80%
bowing and scraping

00:36:19.560 --> 00:36:21.390 line:80%
to flatter the powerful.

00:36:23.390 --> 00:36:24.280 line:80%
What a pity.

00:36:24.470 --> 00:36:26.680 line:80%
I won't be there for my nephew's birth.

00:36:26.680 --> 00:36:27.680 line:80%
Niece.

00:36:28.160 --> 00:36:29.280 line:80%
You prefer girls.

00:36:31.080 --> 00:36:31.800 line:80%
He,

00:36:32.080 --> 00:36:33.680 line:80%
you are more well-read than I am.

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:35.430 line:80%
Give your niece a name.

00:36:35.910 --> 00:36:38.800 line:80%
Why not let your lord name her?

00:36:39.600 --> 00:36:41.470 line:80%
The Lieutenant General's rank is too high.

00:36:41.470 --> 00:36:43.670 line:80%
I fear the child can't bear such weight.

00:36:45.430 --> 00:36:47.030 line:80%
What should it be?

00:36:47.760 --> 00:36:49.240 line:80%
What is suitable?

00:36:51.470 --> 00:36:52.510 line:80%
Changyu.

00:36:52.870 --> 00:36:53.830 line:80%
Changyu.

00:36:53.830 --> 00:36:54.470 line:80%
Right.

00:36:55.680 --> 00:36:57.870 line:80%
"Long may I stay by your side,

00:36:58.030 --> 00:37:00.280 line:80%
where jade steps bloom with springtide."

00:37:00.280 --> 00:37:00.940 line:80%
How is that?

00:37:02.310 --> 00:37:02.970 line:80%
Wonderful.

00:37:03.600 --> 00:37:04.680 line:80%
That is a good name.

00:37:07.170 --> 00:37:12.480 line:80%
[Lucheng]

00:37:09.720 --> 00:37:10.800 line:80%
Wei,

00:37:12.030 --> 00:37:14.430 line:80%
you have a good daughter.

00:37:15.200 --> 00:37:18.280 line:80%
She is loyal, righteous, and brave.

00:37:20.720 --> 00:37:22.760 line:80%
I really envy you.

00:37:50.830 --> 00:37:52.230 line:80%
The longer the war lasts,

00:37:52.510 --> 00:37:54.640 line:80%
the harder it is for the people.

00:37:55.600 --> 00:37:57.560 line:80%
Corpses of the starved line the roads,

00:37:57.560 --> 00:37:59.620 line:80%
and refugees come one after another.

00:37:59.910 --> 00:38:02.600 line:80%
To end the war with the fewest casualties,

00:38:03.030 --> 00:38:04.470 line:80%
even if one kills,

00:38:05.160 --> 00:38:08.200 line:80%
it is still an act of great benevolence.

00:38:17.720 --> 00:38:19.910 line:80%
Since there have never been
female generals in the camp,

00:38:19.910 --> 00:38:21.560 line:80%
I had a suit

00:38:21.560 --> 00:38:23.230 line:80%
custom-made for you.

00:38:27.310 --> 00:38:30.470 line:80%
May it accompany you
to gain fame and glory.

00:38:42.160 --> 00:38:44.910 line:80%
The last time I felt this uneasy

00:38:46.720 --> 00:38:50.160 line:80%
was in Jinzhou 17 years ago.

00:38:58.470 --> 00:39:00.560 line:80%
Beat the drums! Muster the troops!

00:39:02.200 --> 00:39:06.200 line:80%
-Beat the drums! Muster the troops!
-Beat the drums! Muster the troops!

00:39:14.040 --> 00:39:20.010 line:80%
[Lucheng]

00:39:29.640 --> 00:39:30.240 line:80%
Go.

00:39:36.830 --> 00:39:37.890 line:80%
Stop the carriage!

00:39:46.030 --> 00:39:47.870 line:80%
Soldiers of the Jizhou Army!

00:39:48.080 --> 00:39:48.950 line:80%
-Here!
-Here!

00:39:49.830 --> 00:39:51.910 line:80%
If the city stands, I stand!

00:39:51.910 --> 00:39:53.950 line:80%
If the city falls, I fall!

00:39:53.950 --> 00:39:56.030 line:80%
-If the city stands, I stand!
-If the city stands, I stand!

00:39:56.030 --> 00:39:58.960 line:80%
-If the city falls, I fall!
-If the city falls, I fall!

00:40:00.260 --> 00:40:02.440 line:80%
[Lucheng]

00:40:11.120 --> 00:40:11.800 line:80%
Qianqian,

00:40:13.510 --> 00:40:14.390 line:80%
General Qi

00:40:14.800 --> 00:40:16.600 line:80%
will escort you safely to Lin'an

00:40:17.280 --> 00:40:19.340 line:80%
to meet up with Changning and Bao'er.

00:40:19.950 --> 00:40:22.150 line:80%
I must stay here and stand with Lucheng.

00:40:22.950 --> 00:40:23.760 line:80%
Mrs. Fan,

00:40:24.600 --> 00:40:26.120 line:80%
His Lordship is on the battlefield.

00:40:26.120 --> 00:40:28.080 line:80%
With His Lordship
and the Counselor's strategy,

00:40:28.080 --> 00:40:29.800 line:80%
I believe they will surely defend Lucheng.

00:40:29.800 --> 00:40:32.400 line:80%
Besides, Changning
is waiting for you at home.

00:40:34.080 --> 00:40:35.210 line:80%
I've fought in wars.

00:40:36.200 --> 00:40:38.390 line:80%
I know how terrifying the battlefield is.

00:40:38.390 --> 00:40:39.390 line:80%
But I also know

00:40:39.720 --> 00:40:40.990 line:80%
that if Lucheng falls,

00:40:41.310 --> 00:40:42.710 line:80%
Jizhou will be in danger.

00:40:43.240 --> 00:40:44.390 line:80%
If Jizhou is in danger,

00:40:44.390 --> 00:40:46.600 line:80%
the rebels can march straight
to the Capital.

00:40:46.600 --> 00:40:48.130 line:80%
Then, as big as the world is,

00:40:48.680 --> 00:40:49.950 line:80%
where would I hide?

00:40:51.520 --> 00:40:53.180 line:80%
Where would Changning hide?

00:40:55.390 --> 00:40:56.770 line:80%
And where would

00:40:58.280 --> 00:40:59.740 line:80%
the people of Lin'an hide?

00:41:01.120 --> 00:41:01.990 line:80%
I support you.

00:41:03.510 --> 00:41:06.510 line:80%
You are the most capable female warrior
I've ever met.

00:41:06.690 --> 00:41:07.890 line:80%
Follow your heart.

00:41:09.080 --> 00:41:10.740 line:80%
If you want to stay, then stay.

00:41:11.640 --> 00:41:12.800 line:80%
Don't worry about me.

00:41:12.800 --> 00:41:14.130 line:80%
Once I'm back in Lin'an,

00:41:14.390 --> 00:41:15.760 line:80%
I will protect Changning,

00:41:15.760 --> 00:41:17.220 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, and the others.

00:41:17.510 --> 00:41:18.480 line:80%
If you must go,

00:41:19.870 --> 00:41:20.800 line:80%
then go.

00:41:24.560 --> 00:41:26.390 line:80%
Don't worry. We'll go with her.

00:41:28.030 --> 00:41:29.160 line:80%
Behind us

00:41:30.720 --> 00:41:32.580 line:80%
lies Lin'an that we must protect.

00:41:34.630 --> 00:41:35.230 line:80%
Changyu.

00:41:36.390 --> 00:41:37.550 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:41:37.580 --> 00:41:38.600 line:80%
We'll go too.

00:41:38.600 --> 00:41:39.390 line:80%
We'll go too.

00:41:40.910 --> 00:41:43.400 line:80%
Changyu, I used to be a coward,

00:41:43.990 --> 00:41:46.640 line:80%
because I wanted to go back alive
to see my grandmother.

00:41:46.640 --> 00:41:47.640 line:80%
But she's dead.

00:41:47.640 --> 00:41:49.240 line:80%
Now I just want to avenge her.

00:41:49.310 --> 00:41:50.950 line:80%
Changyu, you are not alone.

00:41:51.310 --> 00:41:52.280 line:80%
I'll go with you!

00:41:52.800 --> 00:41:53.720 line:80%
I'll go with you too!

00:41:53.720 --> 00:41:54.400 line:80%
Me too!

00:41:54.430 --> 00:41:55.040 line:80%
Me too!

00:41:55.070 --> 00:41:55.710 line:80%
Me too!

00:41:55.730 --> 00:41:56.210 line:80%
Me too!

00:41:56.240 --> 00:41:57.170 line:80%
-Me too!
-Me too!

00:42:01.950 --> 00:42:02.720 line:80%
Soldiers,

00:42:03.510 --> 00:42:05.710 line:80%
today, I, Fan Changyu, give you my word.

00:42:06.990 --> 00:42:08.990 line:80%
I will live or die with Lucheng!

00:42:08.990 --> 00:42:10.080 line:80%
-Live or die together!
-Live or die together!

00:42:10.080 --> 00:42:12.160 line:80%
-Defend Lucheng! Live or die together!
